  emsenn:Featuredtexts &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/philosophy-of-endeavor/> , &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/the-settlement-path/> , &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/temporality-of-endeavors/> , &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/formal-structure-of-office/> , &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/algebraic-structure-of-work/> ;
